<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Anoint" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Anoint</orth> (cf. <emph>'noint</emph>), to overspread with a liquid substance: <cit><quote>a. his eyes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.261" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 261</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll a. my sword,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 141</bibl></cit>. Especially to consecrate by unction: <bibl n="shak. lll 3.184" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.523" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 523</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.358" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 358</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.98" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.96" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 96</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.127.55" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 127</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 3, 40</bibl>. H4B Ind. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 3, 40</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5.91" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 5, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 1, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 1, 17</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">3, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.150" default="NO" valid="yes">4, 150</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.124" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 124</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.7.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 7, 58</bibl> (always in the partic. <emph>anointed</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>